properties.headline: FLOODING - NARROMINE SHIRE COUNCIL various roads
properties.otherAdvice:
All unsealed roads signposted "IMPASSABLE IN WET WEATHER" in the Shire are closed to all vehicles.

All other unsealed roads in the Shire are closed to all vehicles over 3.5 tonne.

For an update on local road closures please contact Narromine Shire Council’s office on (02) 6889 9999 or go to their website.

properties.headline: FLOODING - WARRUMBUNGLE SHIRE COUNCIL various roads
properties.otherAdvice:
Some roads in the shire are closed or affected by water.
For an update on local road closures please contact Council’s office on (02) 6849 2000 or see the website link.

properties.headline: FLOODING - HILLSTON TO BOOLIGAL Lachlan Valley Way
properties.otherAdvice:
Other roads closed in the shire:

  • Gunbar Booligal Rd
  • Mossgiel Rd (Hillston to Mossgiel)
  • Carrathool Rd
  • Whealbah Rd (north of MR80 Mossgiel Rd to National Park entrance)
  • Roto Rd

Any roads which are not sealed are dry weather access only.

For more detailed information on local roads, call the Carrathool Shire Council on (02) 6965 1900. After hours updates are available on 0407 244 429.

properties.headline: FLOODING - LACHLAN SHIRE COUNCIL various roads
properties.otherAdvice:
All unsealed roads within Lachlan Shire are closed to vehicles over 3 tonnes until 11.00am Friday 30 October 2020, when the condition of the roads will be reviewed.

School buses, Council road repair plant and Emergency Services are exempt, subject to normal risk assessment.

For an update on local road closures please contact Council’s office on (02) 6895 1950 or see the website link.
